{"tid":270744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支聯會：11萬人參加集會，出年維園見！","createTime":"2017-06-04T13:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T00:16:20.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf1c27af3eaccd3e6e1f876a7cbe284fae2106e","tid":270744,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1334151_1_L_20170604214624.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1334151_1_L_20170604214624.jpg&h=74c60340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支聯會在維園舉行的六四燭光悼念集會，主席何俊仁表示有約11萬人參與晚會，坐滿6個足球場及至少一半草地範圍。<br />\n<br />\n何俊仁誦讀大會宣言，又表示香港市民以堅定的意志每年今夜進行集會，呼籲要繼續肩負守護六四事件真相的責任，堅信香港以至內地曾經歷事件的人有共同記憶，拒絕遺忘。<br />\n<br />\n何俊仁表示，回歸20周年，中共一直在港打壓民主人權，干預香港事務，將專政一套加諸香港，但希望港人堅持站在民主、人權、自由的最前線，團結中國人民，結束一黨專政，相信六四事件必將平反，專政必會結束，民主憲政會戰勝歸來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a597a45f7da4c828ed0cf3d0305a25551b0363","tid":270744,"uid":4242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:53:13.000Z","msg":"今年收左幾多捐款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d51149bd08de155d8e3fab104f33d15c540eaac","tid":270744,"uid":91667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:54:54.000Z","msg":"11萬個 &quot;on99&quot; 無野做囉"},{"pid":"376678adce3f8accfa7ef9499bd5070f33bdb6ec","tid":270744,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:55:36.000Z","msg":"少過舊年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810d0d6108d88bc7e56eab24a0fc9db379767a93","tid":270744,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/0